BEGIN_PGML

[@ image( "UBC-SM-18-045.png", width=>[$width], height=>[$height]) @]*

A rectangular piece of wood, [`[$h]`]x[`[$w]`] [`mm`] cross-section, supports a tensile load of [`[$f]`] [`N`]. Determine the normal and shear stresses that act perpendicular and parallel to the wood grain. The grain is inclined [`[$thetaD]^{\circ}`] to the length of the wood piece. 

[`\sigma_x=`] [____]{"$sigmaX"} [`kPa`]  
[`\sigma_y=`] [____]{"$sigmaY"} [`kPa`]  
[`\tau_{xy}=`] [____]{"$tau"} [`kPa`]  

END_PGML

